The '''Cavemouth''' is an unused non-player character added with Canoeing. Presumably, it was intended to be a piece of interactive scenery that the player sees during the [[Canoe]] cutscene, similar to Trees and Bullrushes. The name suggests it would have been seen when travelling through the cave to the Wilderness pond using a Waka canoe. For unknown reasons however, the Cavemouth can never be seen ingame.
